id: pmc-4a7j
title: Adopt ItemMetadata SDK reader after pm-cli terminology migration
description: Replace pm-changelog imports and documentation of the removed listAllFrontMatter SDK export with listAllItemMetadata so the published extension activates against pm-cli's canonical TOON metadata API and pm-cli release gates remain ecosystem-safe.
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 0
tags[4]: compatibility,metadata,pm-cli,sdk
created_at: "2026-07-12T20:59:36.482Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-12T21:17:29.681Z"
author: codex-frontmatter-vocabulary
resolution: Fixed by migrating the extension runtime to listAllItemMetadata.
expected_result: Published pm-changelog activates against the renamed pm-cli SDK and its commands remain available.
actual_result: Source and dist artifacts use listAllItemMetadata; local pm-cli package activation and all 108 package tests pass.
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-12T21:01:05.591Z",codex-frontmatter-vocabulary,"Evidence: pm-cli PR #531 Gates (static) failed because published pm-changelog imported removed listAllFrontMatter. Updated source and built extension artifacts to listAllItemMetadata and item metadata wording; installed the local pm-cli PR package without saving dependency changes; npm build passed and all 108 tests passed, including package install/activation coverage."
  "2026-07-12T21:17:29.681Z",codex-frontmatter-vocabulary,"Bridge correction: the first transition release used a named legacy SDK import, which new pm-cli correctly rejects before aliasing. Replaced it with namespace feature detection that prefers listAllItemMetadata and only constructs the published fallback name at runtime; this supports both rollout sides without restoring an obsolete pm-cli export."
files[3]{path,scope,note}:
  dist/extension.js,project,Published extension build output
  dist/extension.js.map,project,Published extension source map
  src/extension.ts,project,Adopt canonical pm SDK metadata reader
tests[2]{command,scope,timeout_seconds,note}:
  "npm run release:check",project,600,Full package release gate
  npm test,project,300,Package build and 108-test suite against local pm-cli PR SDK
body: ""
